Nasaan ang Linglongmi ko?

684
00:41:10,160 --> 00:41:11,000
Ibalik mo ito sa iyo

685
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:13,120
Hindi ko sinasadyang kunin

686
00:41:14,720 --> 00:41:15,560
Kapatid na Zhan

687
00:41:15,640 --> 00:41:16,520
Itabi mo

688
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:17,880
Ang napakasarap na pulot na ito

689
00:41:17,960 --> 00:41:18,880
Siguraduhing panatilihin itong maayos

690
00:41:19,120 --> 00:41:20,840
- Kaya... - Nagsisinungaling siya.

691
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:21,920
Partikular na para lokohin ako

692
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:23,120
Hindi mo man lang ito makita

693
00:41:26,160 --> 00:41:27,200
Karapat-dapat kang lokohin

694
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:28,640
Hindi ba't curious lang ako?

695
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:30,800
Nabalitaan ko na ang pulot-pukyutan ng Linglong ay isang mahimalang gamot.

696
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:32,520
Sa ibang araw, masasaktan ako at susubukan ko ulit

697
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:34,520
Ito ay gamot

698
00:41:34,600 --> 00:41:36,480
Nagmamadali ka pa ring kumain, may sakit ka ba?

699
00:41:36,560 --> 00:41:37,640
Sabi ninyong lahat may sakit ako

700
00:41:37,720 --> 00:41:39,080
Kung gayon, dapat akong uminom ng ilang tableta pa

701
00:41:39,360 --> 00:41:41,320
Nakain ba ni Zhan Zhao ang lahat ng masasarap na bagay?

702
00:41:48,240 --> 00:41:49,080
Tumatawa?

703
00:41:49,920 --> 00:41:51,520
Huwag kang magalit kung tatawa ka

704
00:41:51,600 --> 00:41:53,800
Mula ngayon, kailangan mo na akong tawaging Kuya Bai ulit.

705
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:55,680
Ilang taon ka na ngayong taon?

706
00:41:55,760 --> 00:41:56,760
Anim sa dalawampu

707
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:57,920
Kung gayon, mas matanda ako sa iyo

708
00:41:58,400 --> 00:42:00,560
Xiaobai, huwag mo akong tawaging Kuya Bai.

709
00:42:00,640 --> 00:42:02,640
Sa itsura mo, paano mo masasabing mas matanda ka sa akin?

710
00:42:02,720 --> 00:42:03,920
Dapat may hangganan ang pagsasalita ng mga walang kwentang bagay, 'di ba?

711
00:42:05,560 --> 00:42:07,360
Pwede ka bang magsalita ng walang kwentang bagay, pero ako hindi?

712
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:09,440
Ayaw mo ba sa pangalang Xiaobai?

713
00:42:09,880 --> 00:42:11,760
Pagkatapos ay mga puting daga, si Lao Bai

714
00:42:11,840 --> 00:42:13,400
Bai Yutang, Bai Mouzi

715
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:14,360
Pumili ka ng isa

716
00:42:14,760 --> 00:42:15,640
Tumatawa ka pa rin

717
00:42:17,880 --> 00:42:19,520
Minamaliit talaga kita

718
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:21,280
Hindi ko inaasahan na marami kang mga panlilinlang na nasa iyong manggas

719
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:24,760
Tinatanong kita

720
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:26,760
Pumasok ka sa palasyo nang gabing iyon

721
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:29,360
Para lang talaga humingi ng mga block token na ilabas

722
00:42:29,600 --> 00:42:30,440
Wala nang iba?

723
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:32,720
Wala nang iba pa

724
00:42:33,160 --> 00:42:34,240
Magpahinga nang maayos

725
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:42,600
Kung ito ay matuklasan

726
00:42:42,680 --> 00:42:43,920
Kailangan nating lahat mawalan ng ulo

727
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:45,280
Ano ang magagawa natin?

728
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:46,640
Medyo matingkad ito

729
00:42:46,720 --> 00:42:48,600
Gaano na ba katagal? May pakialam ka pa rin ba kung maganda ito o hindi?

730
00:43:01,280 --> 00:43:02,120
(Zhao Zhen, Emperador)

731
00:43:02,200 --> 00:43:03,040
panatilihin ito

732
00:43:03,560 --> 00:43:04,520
Napakaganda
